  Additionally, Mugo is blessed with a very high CHA with items and buffs he can get to 255.  Ironically, you get the best prices when your CHA is at 110 or above, and your faction is ally.  So be sure to buy all your components from vendors in your home city if possible, or some place where your name is synonomous with 'saviour of the city.'<br>
  Some skills depend on other stats too, like STR for smithing.  Find out what stat most affects the skill you are working on, then find a nice shammy and reward them for their buffs, you will benefit from it.  Note: I have noticed a high AGI increases your chances of combining research components, throw in a high WIS and your odds are far better than without.<br>
<br>
Aev.<br>
